entry.title: Complete Dabbing Bundle #2
entry.summary:
Vendor: the dabbing specialists
Type: Complete Dabbing Kit
Price: 86.00

Complete Dabbing Bundle #2

[click to view our shipping policies]

Description for part number 1134

The flat-top quartz banger design combined with drop-in insert cups is a relatively new addition to the dab scene. The biggest feature advantage is that the drop-in cup insert helps keep your banger looking like new! This setup allows you to either heat the banger up as you normally would, and then drop the loaded cup insert in, or you can heat the insert cup up, drop it in with tweezers, and then insert your wax like you normally would. We prefer to heat the banger up like we normally would and then drop the loaded cup into the banger. You'll keep your banger looking much cleaner and you'll experience amazing terp profiles as the cup insert shields your concentrates from high heat levels while also ensuring complete vaporization.

Bundle Includes:

  • (1) Quartz Banger Flat Top 14mm Female With Cup Insert and Saucer Cap (14mm Female)
  • (1) Reborn Mini Dual Bubbler (14mm Male Joint)
  • (1) Professional Quality Butane Blow Torch (Auto-Ignition / Piezo Ignition) [Butane Not Included]
